# Line-ending policy.
#
# spec/11 requires canonical LF with a final newline, and spec/14 records
# line-ending semantics as source identity. Leaving normalization to each
# developer's core.autocrlf setting makes byte-level contracts and
# newline-sensitive tooling platform-dependent, so checkout is pinned to LF
# on every platform.

* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets must never be newline-normalized.
*.webp binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.bin binary
